\c 12
\s Miriami anorohwa nemaperembudzi nokuti iye naAroni vakamukira Mozisi
\p
\v 1 Zvino Miriami naAroni vakataura vachipokana naMozisi nekuda kwemukadzi muItiyopiya waaiva awana; nokuti waiva awana mukadzi muItiyopiya\x + Eki. 2.21.\x*.
\v 2 Zvino vakati: Zvirokwazvo Jehovha wakataura naMozisi oga here? Haana kutaurawo nesu here\x + Eki. 4.15; 7.1,2; 15.20. Mik. 6.4.\x*? Jehovha ndoku\add zvi\add*nzwa\x + Gen. 29.33. Num. 11.1; 2 Madz. 19.4. Isa. 37.4. Eze. 35.12,13.\x*.
\v 3 Zvino murume Mozisi waiva munyoro kwazvo kupfuura vanhu vose vaiva pachiso chenyika\x + Map. 76.9.\x*.
\v 4 Zvino Jehovha wakataura pakarepo kuna Mozisi nekuna Aroni nekuna Miriami: Budirai imwi vatatu kutende rekusangana. Vatatu ndokubuda\x + Map. 76.9.\x*.
\v 5 Zvino Jehovha wakaburuka mushongwe yegore, ndokumira \add pa\add*mukova wetende, ndokudana Aroni naMiriami; ivo vaviri vakabuda\x + 11.25; 16.19.\x*.
\v 6 Zvino wakati: Inzwai ikozvino mashoko angu; kana kune muporofita \add pakati\add* penyu, \add ini\add* Jehovha ndichazvizivisa kwaari nechiratidzo\x + Gen. 46.2. Eze. 1.1. Dhan. 10.8,16. Gen. 15.1. Dhan. 8.2. Ruk. 1.11,22. Mab. 10.11,17. 22.17,18.\x*, ndichataura naye muhope\x + Gen. 31.10,11. 1 Madz. 3.5. Job. 33.15. Mat. 1.20.\x*.
\v 7 Muranda wangu Mozisi haana kudaro\x + Map. 105.26.\x*; wakatendeka\x + VaHeb. 3.2,5.\x* paimba yangu yose\x + 1 Tim. 3.15.\x*.
\v 8 Ndinotaura naye muromo nemuromo\x + Eki. 33.11. Num. 7.89. Det. 34.10; 1 VaKori. 13.12.\x*, uye pachena, uye kwete munhaurwa dzisinganzwisisiki\x + Vato. 14.12; Map. 49.4; 78.2. Zvir. 1.6.\x*; uye achaona chimiro chaJehovha\x + Eki. 33.19.\x*; naizvozvo sei maiva musingatyi kutaura muchipokana nemuranda wangu, muchipokana naMozisi\x + 12.7.\x*?
\v 9 Zvino hasha dzaJehovha dzakavapfutira, iye ndokubva.
\v 10 Zvino gore rakabva patende; zvino tarira, Miriami\x + Det. 24.9.\x* ava nemaperembudzi\x + 2 Madz. 5.27. Rev. 13.10; 2 Madz. 15.5; 2 Makor. 26.19,20.\x*, semagada echando; Aroni ndokutarira kuna Miriami, zvino, tarira ava nemaperembudzi.
\v 11 Zvino Aroni wakati kuna Mozisi: Haiwa, ishe wangu, musaisa henyu chivi pamusoro pedu, chatakaita upenzi nacho uye chatakatadza nacho\x + 2 Zvak. 19.19; 24.10. Zvir. 30.32.\x*.
\v 12 Ngaarege kuva sewakafa, anoti kana achibuda mudumbu ramai vake hafu yenyama yake yakadyiwa.
\v 13 Zvino Mozisi wakachema kuna Jehovha achiti: Haiwa Mwari, muporesei henyu.
\v 14 Jehovha ndokuti kuna Mozisi: Dai baba vake vaiva vamuisa mate kwazvo pachiso chake\x + Det. 25.9. Job. 30.10.\x*, angadai asina kunyara mazuva manomwe here? Ngaavharirwe panze pemusasa mazuva manomwe\x + Rev. 13.46.\x*, shure kweizvozvo ngaagamuchirwe\add zve\add*.
\v 15 Zvino Miriami wakavharirwa kunze kwemusasa mazuva manomwe; vanhu ndokusafamba kusvika Miriami\x + 2 Makor. 26.20,21. Ruk. 17.12.\x* agamuchirwa\add zve\add*.
\v 16 Zvino shure kweizvozvo vanhu vakabva paHazeroti\x + 11.35; 33.18.\x* ndokudzika matende murenje reParani\x + Gen. 21.21. Num. 10.12; 13.3,26. 1 Zvak. 25.1.\x*.